{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"67dc7500b6","title":"毛泽东、姚文元关于夺权问题的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b624be2f6d","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":23,"articleId":"67dc7500b6"}],"tags":[{"id":"1ae024ca96","name":"革命大联合","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"56a499f88d","name":"上海文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"92a8a42842","name":"姚文元","type":"人物"},{"id":"aa048f8141","name":"夺权","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"ef71f03227","name":"中央文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"yaowenyuan","name":"姚文元文录","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"姚文元","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/姚文元文录.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"45f848c5df","name":"姚文元"}]},"publication_details":{"yaowenyuan":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b73a02811b","type":"title","text":"毛泽东、姚文元关于夺权问题的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"yaowenyuan","articleId":"67dc7500b6"},{"id":"450b992364","type":"paragraph","text":"〖一月二十四日上午十一时五分驻市委北航红旗战士许志新来电话：昨天上海联络站来电话，张春桥同志给中央文革打电话，就夺权问题毛主席和姚文元同志做了如下回答，大意如下。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"yaowenyuan","articleId":"67dc7500b6"},{"id":"a2934d690e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席：如果权落在右派手里，权本来就在右派手里，夺过来。如果再被别人夺去，仍然在右派手里，没有什么了不起，还可以再夺权。","index":2,"publicationId":"yaowenyuan","articleId":"67dc7500b6"},{"id":"69a64bd344","type":"paragraph","text":"姚文元：要搞大联合，要我们做出榜样来，我们自己去闯，闯出一条路来。不要学过去那样试探试探，不要有那些框框，跳出那些框框，大胆去干。上海正准备筹备上海公社，望北京走在他们前边。","index":3,"publicationId":"yaowenyuan","articleId":"67dc7500b6"}],"page":{"id":"1d782b7d68","publicationId":"yaowenyuan","articleId":"67dc7500b6","start":261,"end":261}}}},"__N_SSG":true}